reviewText: A fun film, certainly.  If you enjoy Sonja Henie films, then you'll enjoy this one too.  Olga San Juan is very funny.  This is taken from a 16mm print and is MOD, so it's not the highest quality, but it's certainly very watchable, with a clear enough picture and sound.  Just don't expect a pristine print.  Honestly, I was expecting much worse, so I was very pleasantly surprised by the quality.  Until we get a mastering from Universal, this is an excellent stopgap.
